<c74object name='sp.concatplayer~' category='' module='SP-Tools'>
    <digest>Granular playback engine</digest>
    <description>Granular playback engine for concatenative synthesis.</description>
    <discussion>    <h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
    <p>The <o>sp.concatplayer~</o> object is the underlying playback engine for <o>sp.concatsynth~</o>. It is a stripped-back granular synth engine that plays back small and windowed fragments of a single large <o>buffer~</o> unlike the corpus-based playback elsewhere in SP-Tools.</p>
</discussion>

	<metadatalist>
		<metadata name='author'>Rodrigo Constanzo, Flucoma Project</metadata>
		<metadata name='tag'>Machine Learning</metadata>
		<metadata name='tag'>Drums</metadata>
	</metadatalist>

    <!-- INLETS -->
    <inletlist>
        <inlet id='0' type='list'>
            <digest>Position and <o>buffer~</o> to play from</digest>
            <description>Position (offset in <b>ms</b>) and <o>buffer~</o> name to play back from.</description>
        </inlet>
    </inletlist>
    <!-- INLETS -->

    <!-- OUTLETS -->
    <outletlist>
        <outlet id='0' type='signal'>
            <digest>Audio output (left)</digest>
            <description>Audio output (left).</description>
        </outlet>
        <outlet id='1' type='signal'>
            <digest>Audio output (right)</digest>
            <description>Audio output (right).</description>
        </outlet>
    </outletlist>
    <!-- OUTLETS -->

    <!-- ARGUMENTS -->
    <objarglist>
    </objarglist>
    <!-- ARGUMENTS -->

    <!--MESSAGES-->
    <methodlist>
	</methodlist>
	<!--MESSAGES-->

	<!--ATTRIBUTES-->
	<attributelist>
        <attribute 
        name='rate' 
        type='float' 
        size='1'
        get='1' set='1' 
        >
        <digest>Rate of concatenation</digest>
        <description>Rate of matching/playback in <b>ms</b> in the concatenation engine.</description>

        <attributelist>
            <attribute 
            name='default' 
            type='float' 
            size='1' 
            value='100'
            get='1' set='1' 
            />
        </attributelist>
        </attribute>
        <attribute 
        name='size' 
        type='float' 
        size='1'
        get='1' set='1' 
        >
        <digest>Size of grain to play back</digest>
        <description>Size of grain to play back, in %.</description>

        <attributelist>
            <attribute 
            name='default' 
            type='float' 
            size='1' 
            value='100'
            get='1' set='1' 
            />
        </attributelist>
        </attribute>
        <attribute 
        name='speed' 
        type='float' 
        size='1'
        get='1' set='1' 
        >
        <digest>Playback speed</digest>
        <description>Sets the playback speed for each individual grain.</description>

        <attributelist>
            <attribute 
            name='default' 
            type='float' 
            size='1' 
            value='100'
            get='1' set='1' 
            />
        </attributelist>
        </attribute>
        <attribute 
        name='steal' 
        type='int' 
        size='1'
        get='1' set='1' 
        >
        <digest>Whether poly voice stealing is enabled</digest>
        <description>Sets whether voice stealing is enabled, which allows new samples to start when previous ones are still sounding.</description>

        <attributelist>
            <attribute 
            name='default' 
            type='int' 
            size='1' 
            value='1'
            get='1' set='1' 
            />
        </attributelist>
        </attribute>
        <attribute 
        name='width' 
        type='float' 
        size='1'
        get='1' set='1' 
        >
        <digest>Panning width</digest>
        <description>Sets the random distribution width for the grain panning.</description>

        <attributelist>
            <attribute 
            name='default' 
            type='float' 
            size='1' 
            value='100'
            get='1' set='1' 
            />
        </attributelist>
        </attribute>
        <attribute 
        name='window' 
        type='symbol' 
        size='1'
        get='1' set='1' 
        >
        <digest>Window function for playback</digest>
        <description>Sets the window function for the grain playback."
The available options are:<br/>
<b>sine</b><br/>
<b>hann</b><br/>
<b>triangle</b><br/>
<b>rampdown</b><br/>
<b>rampup</b><br/>
<b>onset</b><br/>
<b>hamming</b><br/>
<b>blackman</b><br/>
<b>square</b>
</description>

        <attributelist>
            <attribute 
            name='default' 
            type='symbol' 
            size='1' 
            value='sine'
            get='1' set='1' 
            />
        </attributelist>
        </attribute>
        <attribute 
        name='voices' 
        type='int' 
        size='1'
        get='1' set='1' 
        >
        <digest>Amount of polyphony</digest>
        <description>Sets the amount of polyphony available for sample playback.</description>

        <attributelist>
            <attribute 
            name='default' 
            type='int' 
            size='1' 
            value='64'
            get='1' set='1' 
            />
        </attributelist>
        </attribute>
	</attributelist>
